divs: Sighting Detailsthis UFO flying above the mosque tower, this event exactly happen at early morning about 4.30am, when i wanna do a Shubuh prayer. its very clearly, and its my very first time to see something like that... its spin around for a while and gone... just like a light... this thing full of a light... i can only stay still and can't move my sight at that thing... until now..i only tell it to my friends... and i'm so sorry i didn't take a picture of it...
